  "prompt": "Does Mi4i has SD card slot?",
  "response": "Yes, the Xiaomi Mi 4i **does** have a microSD card slot. It supports expandable storage through a microSD card, allowing you to increase the device's storage capacity for photos, videos, apps, and other data. The Mi 4i typically supports microSD cards up to 128 GB, giving you ample space to store your files.\n\n**Key Points:**\n- **Expandable Storage:** Yes, via a microSD card.\n- **Supported Capacity:** Up to 128 GB.\n- **Location:** The microSD card slot is usually combined with the SIM card tray, requiring you to use a dual-slot SIM tray or a separate slot depending on the specific model.\n\nIf you plan to expand your storage, make sure to use a compatible and high-quality microSD card to ensure optimal performance and reliability.",
